FastPattern.description: TCPTrafficAudit Consecutive TCP small segments;ET COMPROMISED Known Compromised or Hostile Host Traffic TCP group;Limit on number of overlapping TCP packets reached; Matching TCP DDOS Rule {TCP}
FastPattern.pattern: snort.*:[^:]+.*(?:Consecutive TCP small segments exceeding threshold|ET COMPROMISED Known Compromised or Hostile Host Traffic TCP group \d+|ET CINS Active Threat Intelligence Poor Reputation IP TCP group \d+|Limit on number of overlapping TCP packets reached|Matching TCP DDOS Rule|ET RBN Known Russian Business Network IP TCP).*{(?:TCP|tcp)}
snort.*:[^:]+.*(?:Fragmentation overlap|ET TOR Known Tor \S+ \(.*\) Node UDP Traffic group \d+).*{(?:UDP|udp)}

FastPattern.description: NetworkSuspicious: Sensitive data;Suspicious no-ip Domain;ET MALWARE Suspicious
FastPattern.pattern: snort.*:[^:]+.*(?:Sensitive Data|Suspicious no-ip Domain|ET MALWARE Suspicious)
